nodes.text: Jeff Anderson (born April 21, 1970) is an American voice actor who voiced the Trandoshan hunter Smug in the Season Three finale of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. He is best known for playing Randal Graves in Kevin Smith's View Askewniverse film series, including Clerks, Clerks: The Animated Series, Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back and Clerks II.
